{"pin":"BH00970","subcodes":[{"code":"BH00970","anchor":"","title":"Lawh-i-Laylatu'l-Quds (Tablet of the Sacred Night - Adrianople)","first_line":"The Most Great Name beareth Me witness! How sad if any man were, in this Day, to rest his heart on the transitory things of this world!","first_line_orig":"سبحانک اللهم یا الهی تشهد و تری کیف ابتلیت بین عبادک بعد الذی مااردت الا الخضوع   ","language":"5","word_count":"850","subjects":"@love, unity, and fellowship among the friends; in the Cause, @call to unity; prohibition of disunity, @detachment; severance; renunciation; patience, @being a source of light; guidance, @human soul as mirror; divine light, attributes within, @humility; meekness; lowliness, @tests and trials; sacrifice and suffering","notes":" \u003ca href=\"https://d9263461.github.io/cl/Baha'i/Others/ROB/V2/Contents.html\"\u003eROB2.164\u003c/a\u003e,  \u003ca href=\"https://d9263461.github.io/cl/Baha'i/Others/ROB/V2/Contents.html\"\u003eROB2.188\u003c/a\u003e,  \u003ca href=\"https://reference.bahai.org/fa/t/o/GS/gs-209.html\"\u003eGSH.209\u003c/a\u003e,  \u003ca href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20070930181707/http://bahai-library.com/resources/leiden.list/leiden.list.html#147\"\u003eLL#147\u003c/a\u003e","translations":[],"writing_refs":[{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"ar","lang_name":"Arabic"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"de","lang_name":"German"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"ko","lang_name":"Korean"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"ro","lang_name":"Romanian"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"ta","lang_name":"Tamil"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"tvl","lang_name":"Tuvalu"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"vi","lang_name":"Vietnamese"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"hu","lang_name":"Hungarian"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"sk","lang